Shape-RegularPolygon version 0.01
=================================

Shape::RegularPolygon is a class that treats the shape of the regular
polygon. This class creates and returns vertex list of specified reg-
ular polygon. It is possible to draw in the regular polygon easily by
combining GD::Polyline etc.

The README is used to introduce the module and provide instructions on
how to install the module, any machine dependencies it may have (for
example C compilers and installed libraries) and any other information
that should be provided before the module is installed.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None

